{"prompt": "Generate a website for a health and wellness app. The website should be dynamic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aura Wellness</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: #e6f2ff; /* Light blue background */\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077cc 0%, #66b3ff 100%); /* Blue gradient */\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 320\"><path fill=\"%23ffffff\" fill-opacity=\"0.3\" d=\"M0,192L30,218.7C60,245,120,320,180,304C240,288,300,192,360,160C420,128,480,160,540,192C600,224,660,256,720,256C780,256,840,224,900,192C960,160,1020,128,1080,128C1140,128,1200,160,1260,160C1320,160,1380,128,1440,96L1440,320L1440,320L1380,320C1320,320,1260,320,1200,320C1140,320,1080,320,1020,320C960,320,900,320,840,320C780,320,720,320,660,320C600,320,540,320,480,320C420,320,360,320,300,320C240,320,180,320,120,320C60,320,30,320,0,320Z\"></path></svg>') bottom center repeat-x;\n            background-size: 150% 100%;\n        }\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .features {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff; /* White background for features */\n        }\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #0077cc; /* Brand blue */\n        }\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* Lighter blue for feature cards */\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #0077cc; /* Brand blue */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #005bb5; /* Darker blue */\n        }\n        .cta {\n            background-color: #0077cc; /* Brand blue */\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n        }\n        .cta h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: white;\n            color: #0077cc; /* Brand blue */\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border-radius: 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid white;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e6f2ff; /* Light blue */\n            color: #005bb5; /* Darker blue */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: #005bb5; /* Darker blue */\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        /* Simple icons using font awesome (you'd typically link this in head) */\n        @font-face {\n            font-family: 'FontAwesome';\n            src: url('//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/fonts/fontawesome-webfont.woff2') format('woff2'), url('//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/fonts/fontawesome-webfont.woff') format('woff');\n            font-weight: normal;\n            font-style: normal;\n        }\n        .fa {\n            display: inline-block;\n            font: normal normal normal 14px/1 FontAwesome;\n            font-size: inherit;\n            text-rendering: auto;\n            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;\n        }\n        .fa-heart:before { content: \"\\f004\"; }\n        .fa-leaf:before { content: \"\\f06c\"; }\n        .fa-dumbbell:before { content: \"\\f44a\"; }\n        .fa-moon:before { content: \"\\f186\"; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Aura Wellness</h1>\n        <p>Find your balance. Nurture your mind, body, and spirit.</p>\n        <a href=\"#download\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\">Get the App</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"features\">\n        <h2>Features to Enhance Your Life</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fa fa-heart\"></i>\n                <h3>Mindfulness & Meditation</h3>\n                <p>Guided sessions to calm your mind and reduce stress.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fa fa-leaf\"></i>\n                <h3>Nutrition Tracking</h3>\n                <p>Log your meals and discover healthier eating habits.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fa fa-dumbbell\"></i>\n                <h3>Fitness Routines</h3>\n                <p>Personalized workouts for all fitness levels.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fa fa-moon\"></i>\n                <h3>Sleep Stories</h3>\n                <p>Drift off to sleep with soothing narratives.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta\">\n        <h2>Ready to Transform Your Wellbeing?</h2>\n        <p>Download Aura Wellness today and start your journey to a healthier, happier you.</p>\n        <a href=\"#download\" class=\"cta-button\">Download Now</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Aura Wellness. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}